description: This common Plezier purrs with a rating of 3, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 15, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 2 for East, 3 for South, and 1 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [15 Votes, Common]
